comments:
Strength: readings and Professor Siu's lecture; 

Weakness and improvement: 1) I hope Professor Siu could consider breaking down the final project into step-to-step and smaller assignments throughout the semester  (e.g., research questions due by Week 3; literature review due by Week 6; etc.) so that we could make steady progress instead of rushing everything in the end. 

2) Re the presentations during the second half of the semester, I hope Professor Siu consider setting a strict time limit (e.g., 10 minute per student) so that we could have enough time for discussing the weekly readings, or scheduling all presentations for the final two weeks.
